# Project Structure

This is a **Turborepo monorepo** using **Bun workspaces**.

- **Package manager**: Bun (see `package.json#packageManager`)
- **Formatting/linting**: Biome (`biome.json`)
- **TypeScript**: shared configs in `tooling/typescript/*`

## Directory Structure (high level)

```
.
├── apps/
│   ├── api/   # Bun + Hono + tRPC server
│   ├── app/   # Product app (Next.js, App Router)
│   ├── inbox/ # Cloudflare Email Routing worker
│   └── web/   # Marketing site (Next.js)
├── packages/
│   ├── analytics/  # OpenPanel client + server helpers
│   ├── db/         # Drizzle schema + DB client
│   ├── email/      # React Email templates
│   ├── jobs/       # Trigger.dev jobs
│   ├── kv/         # Upstash Redis + rate limiting
│   ├── logger/     # Shared pino logger
│   ├── supabase/   # Supabase clients + local project (schemas/migrations/functions)
│   └── ui/         # Shared UI components (shadcn-style)
├── tooling/
│   └── typescript/ # Shared tsconfig presets
├── turbo.json
├── package.json
└── bun.lockb
```

## Most-used commands (repo root)

```bash
bun install
bun dev
bun dev:app
bun dev:web
bun dev:api
bun dev:email
bun dev:supabase

bun run format
bun run lint
bun run typecheck
bun run test

# Supabase
bun migrate
bun seed
bun reset
bun generate
```

